ability_entry(compound_eyes, generation_iii, true, 'Increases moves'' accuracy to 1.3×.', 'This Pokémon''s moves have 1.3× their accuracy. This ability has no effect on the one-hit KO moves (fissure, guillotine, horn drill, and sheer cold). Overworld: If the first Pokémon in the party has this ability, the chance of a wild Pokémon holding a particular item is raised from 50%, 5%, or 1% to 60%, 20%, or 5%, respectively.').
ability_entry(contrary, generation_v, true, 'Inverts stat changes.', 'Whenever this Pokémon''s stats would be raised, they are instead lowered by the same amount, and vice versa.').
