ability_entry(flame_body, generation_iii, true, 'Has a 30% chance of burning attacking Pokémon on contact.', 'Whenever a move makes contact with this Pokémon, the move''s user has a 30% chance of being burned. Overworld: If any Pokémon in the party has this ability, each egg in the party has its hatch counter decreased by 2 (rather than 1) each step cycle, making eggs hatch roughly twice as quickly. This effect does not stack if multiple Pokémon have this ability or magma armor.').
ability_entry(flare_boost, generation_v, true, 'Increases Special Attack to 1.5× when burned.', 'This Pokémon has 1.5× its Special Attack when burned.').
ability_entry(flash_fire, generation_iii, true, 'Protects against fire moves. Once one has been blocked, the Pokémon''s own Fire moves inflict 1.5× damage until it leaves battle.', 'This Pokémon is immune to fire-type moves. Once this Pokémon has been hit by a Fire move, its own Fire moves will inflict 1.5× as much damage until it leaves battle. This ability has no effect while the Pokémon is frozen. The Fire damage bonus is retained even if the Pokémon is frozen and thawed or the ability is lost or disabled. Fire moves will ignore this Pokémon''s substitute. This ability takes effect even on non-damaging moves, i.e. will o wisp.').
ability_entry(flower_gift, generation_iv, true, 'Increases friendly Pokémon''s Attack and Special Defense to 1.5× during strong sunlight.', 'Friendly Pokémon have 1.5× their Attack and Special Defense during strong sunlight if any friendly Pokémon has this ability. Unlike forecast, multitype, and zen mode, this ability is not tied to its Pokémon''s form change; cherrim will switch between its forms even if it loses this ability. As such, this ability also works if obtained by a Pokémon other than Cherrim.').
